disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Triumphant Roar.

effect radius.value: 1000 / 950

blurb.value: Innate: Alistar charging up his roar by stunning or displacing enemy champions or when nearby enemies die. He roars when charged up, healing himself and all nearby allied champions.

description.value: Innate: Alistar gains a stack of Triumph for every enemy champion he stuns or displaces with Pulverize, Headbutt, or Trample, and every time an enemy minion or non-epic monster dies nearby.

description2.value: At 7 Triumph stacks, Alistar consumes them and roars, healing himself for 25 − 161 (based on level) and all nearby allied champions for「 double the amount. 」「 50 − 322 (based on level). 」

description3.value: Alistar roars instantly if a nearby enemy champion or epic monster dies. Once Triumph stacks are consumed Alistar cannot roar again for a short duration, but can still gain stacks.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * Healing occurs simultaneously for Alistar and his allies. There is a VFX projectile (700 missile speed) that cannot be destroyed by Wind Wall and is unrelated to the actual heal. Alistar loses all Triumph stacks upon dying.
notes.description: Displays additional information with effect table to the right.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Headbutt.

target range.value: 650 / 700

blurb.value: Active: Alistar rams a target with his head, dealing magic damage and knocking them back.

description.value: Active: Alistar dashes to the target enemy's location. If the target is still within a certain radius when the dash ends uninterrupted, he deals them magic damage and knocks them back in relation to his original location over 0.75 seconds whilst also stunning them for 1 second.

description2.value: The ability can be dodged if the target moves 400 units away.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * The dash speed depends on the inverse of the distance to the target: If Alistar's radius overlaps with his target's, he will dash with 1200 speed. If Alistar is further from his target than the previous condition, he will dash with (1200  ×  dash distance) / (dash distance - sum of radiuses). At maximum target range, against an enemy with a 65 gameplay radius (median of all champions), Alistar will dash with 1544 speed (reaching his target within 0.429 seconds). Both the lower the dash distance and the larger Alistar and/or his target, the faster the dash becomes; this scales hyperbolically. When Pulverize is buffered during the dash, the knockback distance is reduced to 200 units. The CC duration of the ability can be reduced by up-to 25%  Tenacity, due to airborne not being reducible while the stun is. Headbutt can knock enemies through terrain. The knockback stops short on walls that cannot be surpassed but the disable duration is not changed. The spell indicator for this ability also displays the direction for the knock back relative to Alistar's position.
notes.description: Displays additional information with effect table to the right.

disp_name.description:
Name of the ability
Only necessary if the value differs from Trample.

effect radius.value: 350

blurb.value: Active: Alistar tramples nearby enemy units, ignoring unit collision and gaining stacks if he deals magic damage to enemy champion with Trample. At full stacks his next basic attack against an enemy champion deals additional magic damage and stuns them.

description.value: Active: Alistar becomes ghosted and tramples the ground around him every 0.5 seconds for 5 seconds, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and gaining a Trample stack every time the ability damages at least one enemy champion.

leveling.value: Magic Damage Per Tick:»8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20 (+ 4% AP)«Total Magic Damage:80 / 110 / 140 / 170 / 200 (+ 40% AP)

description2.value: At 5 Trample stacks, Alistar next basic attack within 6 seconds deals 35 − 290 (based on level) bonus magic damage and applies a 1-second stun on-hit to its target.

targeting.description: Permafrost is a single target ability.

affects.description: Permafrost affects enemy champions and large monsters

onhiteffects.description: onhiteffects can be set to 'true', for abilities that apply on-hit effects (from items or other abilities)

occurrence.description: occurrence can either be set to 'hit' or 'attack', and refers to on-hit effects

spellshield.description: spellshield can either be set to true, or written with a custom description.

callforhelp.description: callforhelp determines whether minion aggro will transfer to the caster

additional.description: Displays additional information in a smaller window below the template.

notes.value: * Trample deals persistent area damage damage around Alistar, while the bonus damage on the resulting attack is proc damage. The stun and bonus damage are blocked by spell shields but the base attack damage is not. The attack bonus is consumed if the attack blocked, but not if it is dodged or missed while Alistar is blinded. In all cases, the attack's effects are negated as normal. As it is an on-hit effect, the bonus damage and stun can be applied by Guinsoo's Rageblade's Phantom Hit.
